HextrudORT_HotEnd_E3D MAKE 7
PTFE_Guide Comes with BMG clones
Any 2mm ID PTFE will do		 MAKE 1 Make from 4mm OD PTFE tube:
1 - Using Xacto blade, create internal chamfer in one end.
2 - Cut that end into an arrow shape (try to match the angle from the HextrudORT body where the hobb gears meet.
3 - Insert into HextrudORT body and cut to match internal length of the E3D HeatSink.
